{"tid":2515354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共政府公開宣佈「文革發動」？","createTime":"2021-05-04T02:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T02:52:38.000Z","uid":101392,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"814d8e5f5fb86aa0784bbe4ce9ae49eace4ecbd0","tid":2515354,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSffqtxm1HzsfQCMY6yotMSJtWjQHiLtGSWNJgZFTpRpo?filename=PQqcoYF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQqcoYF.jpg&h=c19fcfa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（「廣播處」處長李百全、「民政事務局」局長徐英偉、前「特首」夫人梁唐青儀）<br />\n<br />\nSource: 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4131438200275102/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F4131438200275102%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=a067a0d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4131438200275102/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【港台五四升旗　李百全未回應刪 YouTube、不續約利君雅】<br />\n<br />\n/三人戴印有「世紀長征」字樣的紫色口罩，身後則有「文革發動」、「澳門回歸」、「世紀長征」等直幡。<br />\n<br />\n/宣言內容包含「愛祖國」、「心繫家國」、「民族共融」、「振興中華」等字眼，卻隻字不提五四運動中廣為提倡的「民主」和「科學」。<br />\n<br />\n/梁唐青儀見記者時表示，將有 100 集有關近代中國歷史紀錄片在港台電視31台播出，當中將包括六四事件及文化大革命。被問到會否擔心節目上載網上一段時間後會被下架，梁唐青儀則表示暫未與港台商討會否將節目上載至 YouTube。/"},{"pid":"a59450c35998b58555f270f6924002ffe0b6c83e","tid":2515354,"uid":151074,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:34:28.000Z","msg":"文革發動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家比較少咁樣講到岀面嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c8f0f019d6f794ce41af97158edfb2dab95b11","tid":2515354,"uid":44646,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"係咪唔識國情既擦鞋仔自把自為？<br />\n至今&quot;文革&quot;都被中共認為唔係好事<br />\n<br />\n同理你唔會在中共官方場合見到紀念&quot;鎮右鎮反&quot;"},{"pid":"55e60d16eddd0c84d513638b2b81210228534556","tid":2515354,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1dfd7708435e6190503b6f250078e6157621595","tid":2515354,"uid":53172,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"文化大革命<br />\n<br />\n正式啟動"},{"pid":"d658e39ca496a6b172bbd79d51973d9355ca89c8","tid":2515354,"uid":294245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:36:35.000Z","msg":"你講到明都好呀"},{"pid":"a0bca753d0a7d5658907a8c921c1357a5f646369","tid":2515354,"uid":2654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:37:04.000Z","msg":"有譚德賽先生，唔使德先生賽先生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19687b73e887370dd53769dcea3311dc26c2b60","tid":2515354,"uid":45788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"講明d好事嚟<br />\n<br />\n好過依家又要做雞又要貞節牌坊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79376468e0508b19829773f598d730547a2e3ce1","tid":2515354,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29c8f0f019d6f794ce41af97158edfb2dab95b11","tid":2515354,"uid":44646,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"係咪唔識國情既擦鞋仔自把自為？<br />\n至今&q